300
00:15:42,080 --> 00:15:42,720
Welcome!

301
00:15:43,480 --> 00:15:44,040
Thanks.

302
00:15:48,440 --> 00:15:49,120
Qingshan,

303
00:15:50,200 --> 00:15:52,080
