306
00:16:15,760 --> 00:16:16,400
Qian’er…

307
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:18,560
Hey!

308
00:16:18,560 --> 00:16:19,440
You scared me!

309
00:16:21,200 --> 00:16:22,480
