318
00:16:38,760 --> 00:16:39,360
Qian’er,

319
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:41,680
it’s upside down.

320
00:16:41,680 --> 00:16:42,120
You…

321
00:16:46,240 --> 00:16:47,040
I didn’t mean that.

322
00:16:50,160 --> 00:16:51,200
Why are you still here?

323
00:16:51,200 --> 00:16:52,000
