361
00:18:26,520 --> 00:18:28,800
But this news will be spread soon.

362
00:18:29,000 --> 00:18:32,280
Then all the Beiling will unite.

363
00:18:34,360 --> 00:18:35,600
Evil Deity,

364
00:18:36,200 --> 00:18:37,560
I can eradicate them.

365
00:18:37,560 --> 00:18:38,320
Don’t bother.

366
00:18:38,760 --> 00:18:40,280
I’ll make someone

367
00:18:40,520 --> 00:18:42,640
to get us rid of those humans.

368
00:18:43,040 --> 00:18:44,920
If it’s not because of my wound,

369
00:18:45,800 --> 00:18:47,600
the Five Sects

370
00:18:48,160 --> 00:18:49,880
