379
00:19:10,680 --> 00:19:12,760
Take good care of the Eye of Source.

380
00:19:13,160 --> 00:19:15,600
That will be good to your wound as well.

381
00:19:16,120 --> 00:19:18,080
As long as I can revive successfully,

382
00:19:18,160 --> 00:19:20,560
Sumeru Pillar, Dragon Clan, power,

383
00:19:20,600 --> 00:19:22,320
