388
00:19:43,400 --> 00:19:45,080
him since five thousand years ago.

389
00:19:45,760 --> 00:19:48,840
She is not inferior to me.

390
00:19:49,100 --> 00:19:52,140
[Deity Tower]

391
00:20:01,380 --> 00:20:05,620
