392
00:20:03,240 --> 00:20:04,040
Father,

393
00:20:04,240 --> 00:20:05,160
I’m here.

394
00:20:21,760 --> 00:20:23,000
My home is there.

395
00:20:23,560 --> 00:20:24,480
I’m leaving now.

396
00:20:25,600 --> 00:20:26,200
