442
00:23:26,840 --> 00:23:27,520
We Mu Territory

443
00:23:27,960 --> 00:23:29,720
are not going to lose a girl.

444
00:23:51,720 --> 00:23:52,480
Dark Blood Spell.

445
00:23:52,600 --> 00:23:53,280
