449
00:24:22,280 --> 00:24:23,920
That was the first time I met Xue God Clan.

450
00:24:24,320 --> 00:24:25,440
They are really fierce and ugly.

451
00:24:26,560 --> 00:24:27,440
But,

452
00:24:27,560 --> 00:24:28,680
