529
00:28:00,240 --> 00:28:01,200
Take the test.

530
00:28:01,720 --> 00:28:02,520
Find Jiuyou.

531
00:28:08,560 --> 00:28:09,400
I got it.

532
00:28:09,960 --> 00:28:10,840
You mean

533
00:28:11,640 --> 00:28:13,560
the Five Sects’ guard

534
00:28:13,760 --> 00:28:14,600
