546
00:28:39,200 --> 00:28:41,240
Qingshan and I had appointment to teach Luo Li to talk.

547
00:28:41,520 --> 00:28:42,200
Bye.

548
00:28:42,920 --> 00:28:43,720
Talk?

549
00:28:45,120 --> 00:28:45,720
Luo Li,

550
00:28:46,120 --> 00:28:47,560
