565
00:29:09,760 --> 00:29:10,360
Luo Li,

566
00:29:10,360 --> 00:29:11,800
if you want to speak an entire sentence,

567
00:29:11,880 --> 00:29:13,120
you have to learn to use

568
00:29:13,280 --> 00:29:14,960
