571
00:29:23,840 --> 00:29:29,160
You, I, he.

572
00:29:29,280 --> 00:29:29,800
See?

573
00:29:29,960 --> 00:29:30,800
I knew it.

574
00:29:31,240 --> 00:29:32,480
